      <title>南非团结政府为投资者加油打气，银行集团称</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/south-africa-s-unity-government-cheers-investors-banking-group-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家银行业集团的负责人表示，南非新联合政府的组建及其推动经济复苏的前景有助于提振市场情绪和投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/south-africa-s-unity-government-cheers-investors-banking-group-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 13:21:58 GMT</pubDate>
