      <title>波兰计划斥资数十亿兹罗提进行民防改造</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/poland-plans-to-spend-billions-of-zloty-on-civil-defense-revamp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在俄罗斯入侵乌克兰之后，欧盟国家波兰正准备投入数十亿兹罗提用于民防建设。]]></description>
